### ════════════════════════════════════════
### HELPDESK API — REST CLIENT TESTS
### Install "REST Client" extension in VS Code
### Click "Send Request" above each ###
### ════════════════════════════════════════

### Switch environment here:
@base = http://localhost:3000/api
# @base = https://helpdesk-api.onrender.com/api

### Paste tokens + IDs after running requests:
@token      = PASTE_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE
@refresh    = PASTE_REFRESH_TOKEN_HERE
@ticket_id  = PASTE_TICKET_ID_HERE
@comment_id = PASTE_COMMENT_ID_HERE
@tech_id    = PASTE_TECH_USER_ID_HERE


### ── HEALTH ─────────────────────────────
GET {{base}}/health


### ── LOGIN (Admin) ──────────────────────
POST {{base}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@company.com",
  "password": "Admin@123"
}


### ── LOGIN (Technician) ─────────────────
POST {{base}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "tech@company.com",
  "password": "Tech@123"
}


### ── LOGIN (User) ───────────────────────
POST {{base}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "employee@company.com",
  "password": "User@123"
}


### ── MY PROFILE ─────────────────────────
GET {{base}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### ── REFRESH TOKEN ───────────────────────
POST {{base}}/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refresh}}"
}


### ── LOGOUT ──────────────────────────────
POST {{base}}/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refresh}}"
}


### ── CREATE TICKET ──────────────────────
### (triggers confirmation email)
POST {{base}}/tickets
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "VPN drops every 30 minutes",
  "description": "Cannot stay connected to company VPN from home office. Error 691 appears after exactly 30 minutes. Windows 11 laptop, HP EliteBook. Started after last Windows update.",
  "priority": "high",
  "category": "network"
}


### ── LIST ALL TICKETS ────────────────────
GET {{base}}/tickets
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### ── FILTER TICKETS ──────────────────────
GET {{base}}/tickets?status=open&priority=high&page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### ── SEARCH TICKETS ──────────────────────
GET {{base}}/tickets?search=VPN
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### ── DASHBOARD STATS ─────────────────────
GET {{base}}/tickets/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### ── GET SINGLE TICKET ───────────────────
GET {{base}}/tickets/{{ticket_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### ── ASSIGN TICKET ────────────────────────
### (triggers assigned email)
PATCH {{base}}/tickets/{{ticket_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "assignedTo": "{{tech_id}}",
  "status": "in_progress"
}


### ── RESOLVE TICKET ───────────────────────
### (triggers resolved email)
PATCH {{base}}/tickets/{{ticket_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "resolved"
}


### ── ADD COMMENT ─────────────────────────
### (triggers comment email)
POST {{base}}/tickets/{{ticket_id}}/comments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "body": "I've picked up this ticket. Investigating the VPN logs now. Can you confirm your Windows build version (Settings → System → About)?",
  "isInternal": false
}


### ── ADD INTERNAL NOTE ────────────────────
POST {{base}}/tickets/{{ticket_id}}/comments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "body": "INTERNAL: This looks related to RADIUS server timeout. Check auth logs on FS-AUTH-01.",
  "isInternal": true
}


### ── LIST USERS (admin only) ─────────────
GET {{base}}/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### ── LIST TECHNICIANS ────────────────────
GET {{base}}/users/technicians
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### ── GET NOTIFICATIONS ───────────────────
GET {{base}}/notifications
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### ── MARK ALL READ ───────────────────────
PUT {{base}}/notifications/read-all
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### ── DELETE TICKET (admin) ──────────────
DELETE {{base}}/tickets/{{ticket_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
